title: Rotating game mode queue now live!

replies.body: I agree that URF should be on rotation more but you don't have to nag riot about it. Without Riot Games we wouldn't even have the game itself so be grateful :) Also there is probably a reason they haven't put URF on as much as the other gamemodes anyway
Everyone constantly complaining about no Doom Bots. It finally comes on so they complain about other stuff? Wtf Riot gave u guys what u said u really wanted and now no one is happy?
Why does it say 3am AEST when it's 2:19am AEST but the queue is gone? I don't think rito realises we went into daylight savings...
We are in AEDT (Australian Eastern Daylight Savings time) AEST is AEST, Doesnt change
urf and doom bots for ever c:
